{assign var="active" value="increase"}

<div class="row login">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="shopyheader">
                <h2>{l s='Features that increase security' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 shopyinfopanel">
                <h2>{l s='Features that increase security' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question1" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question1">
                        {l s='Cookie Law' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse in" id="question1">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="It is essential to ensure that your PrestaShop complies with the regulations applicable to the Cookie Law. With this objective, this functionality allows you to place a totally personalized banner to obtain the user's consent. In this way, you ensure the privacy and security of your customers' data, avoiding possible legal sanctions and protecting the reputation of your company." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/cookies-law/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CpQuPMvhe2I"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Cookies Law banner configuration'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question2" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question2">
                        {l s='Database Cleaner and Optimizer' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question2">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="This tool is essential to maintain optimal performance of your PrestaShop store. You will be able to locate and delete unnecessary data, such as orphaned files, unused connections and browsing data, which will optimize server resources and ensure that your store is always available and fast for your customers. Pre-defining the deadline for eliminations." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/database-cleaner-and-optimizer/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uwg7RDB-vEE"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Cleaning files with Cleaner'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question3" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question3">
                        {l s='User Roles and Traces' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question3">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="The management of the work team is critical in any business, since it is one of the keys to achieve success and increase productivity." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s="With this functionality, you will be able to create users and assign roles to each of your collaborators, defining the options that they will have access to in Shopylinker and in PrestaShop. Plus, thanks to action tracking, you'll always know who performed what action." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/user-roles-and-traces/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question4" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question4">
                        {l s='Enhanced International Sales' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question4">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="With this function, you will be able to issue invoices with total precision in each country and solve the problems that may arise due to the different VAT application criteria. It gives you the possibility of establishing different VAT rates for the same product, being able to apply, for example, basic VAT in one country and reduced VAT in another. In addition, you can check the price of the product with VAT included in the different countries where it is sold." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/improved-international-sales/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question5" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question5">
                        {l s='Automated backups and restores' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question5">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s="A system that will help you protect your business from disasters. It allows you to manually or automatically back up all the information in your online store and restore it with just one click." mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/all-functions/automated-backups-and-restores/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit the explanatory page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a><br>
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OHniP3ZLVrc"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Backup and restore of a store' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a><br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
            {include file="module:shopylinkerp/views/templates/admin/sidebar.tpl" var=active}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
